So you've decided to give Telescope a try, but you're not sure where to begin. Have no fear, this step-by-step guide will show you how to get started. 

### Before We Start

Note that these instructions apply primarily to **Mac OS** (although the instructions below will also work for most Debian/Ubuntu based distributions). If you're using another platform, you may need to tweak them to suit.

Also, if you run into any issues during the process, please make sure you try and troubleshoot the appropriate piece of software (i.e. Git/Node/Meteor/etc.) first before asking for Telescope-specific support here. 

Finally, you might have already installed some of the necessary software, such as Git or Node. So feel free to skip any step of the process as required.

